I&#x27;m not sure I agree with the deepsteg project.  From the website :<p>&quot;Fighting crime online<p>Steganography is used by criminals to send messages to other criminals secretly. It is used by terrorists, pedophiles, and other criminals. Spreading awareness and providing tools to expose hidden data can help fight crime.
&quot;
I can think of several reasons people might use steganography, most involve personal freedom and safety.
